## Quiz Master

Quiz Master is an interactive web application designed to create and participate in quizzes. It's a versatile tool for educators, trainers, and anyone who loves trivia.

 [Try Quiz](https://praful-daksh.github.io/QuizMaster)

## Features

- **Quiz Creation**: Create quizzes with multiple choice questions.
- **Real-time Participation**: Users can participate in quizzes in real-time.
- **Scoring System**: Automatic scoring and feedback.
- **Responsive Design**: Accessible on both desktop and mobile devices.
- **Various Categories**: Various areas of quiz questions.

## Technologies Used

- **HTML**
- **CSS**
- **JAVASCRIPT**
- **API Used**: [Visit Api](https://opentdb.com)
